{"tid":512380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【仆你個街】城大康樂樓慘遭蹂躪  被強行改名為「中國銀行（香港）綜合樓」","createTime":"2017-12-28T12:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T14:00:51.000Z","uid":136994,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2aefeb840f787c0ca2b402f047fcc80011678b5b","tid":512380,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/城大康樂樓冠名-中銀香港綜合樓-學生會斥未諮詢/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%BA%B7%E6%A8%82%E6%A8%93%E5%86%A0%E5%90%8D-%E4%B8%AD%E9%8A%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%B6%9C%E5%90%88%E6%A8%93-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%96%A5%E6%9C%AA%E8%AB%AE%E8%A9%A2%2F&d=8Eiy3MSIFy3n6AHnM7FkettKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fd3df817\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%BA%B7%E6%A8%82%E6%A8%93%E5%86%A0%E5%90%8D-%E4%B8%AD%E9%8A%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%B6%9C%E5%90%88%E6%A8%93-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%96%A5%E6%9C%AA%E8%AB%AE%E8%A9%A2%2F&h=f62f8983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/城大康樂樓冠名-中銀香港綜合樓-學生會斥未諮詢/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/city5-01_WLrB1_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcity5-01_WLrB1_1200x0.png&h=efcaa8aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n城市大學發表新聞稿公佈，為感謝中銀香港慈善基金捐助，城大校方將校園的康樂樓命名為「中國銀行（香港）綜合樓」。學生會幹事會會長不同意有關冠名，批評決定未有諮詢學生意見。<br />\n<br />\n城大校園電視媒體「城市廣播」引述學生會會長陳岳霖指，不同意康樂樓冠名。陳岳霖指，城大學生會屬下各組織辦公室均設於康樂樓，故康樂樓是城大學生會的重要象徵；但冠名程序只由校董會十餘人決定，並未有諮詢學生意見。<br />\n<br />\n城大發表新聞稿，提到中銀香港慈善基金早前捐贈港幣1億元予城大，以支持動物醫學發展、資助冠名講座教授席及學生海外交流和實習。為表彰中銀香港慈善基金對大學的慷慨捐助，城大將康樂樓命名為「中國銀行（香港）綜合樓」。<br />\n<br />\n城大校長郭位感謝中銀香港，並表示「捐款將帶來變革性的影響，推動香港公共衞生、人畜共患病研究、食物安全等發展，有助達致人類、動物及環境的『健康一體化』。」<br />\n<br />\n除學生會屬下各組織，及大學教學及行政部門的辦公室外，該大樓亦設有圖書館、演講廳、學生活動室及餐飲設施等。"},{"pid":"5f543c88ec7e22408c3a0139d78a92efebacfb20","tid":512380,"uid":51978,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"其實唔係盲目反中<br />\n以任何一間銀行冠名大學校園建築物都好不得體<br />\n成浸銅臭味"},{"pid":"926c55f88197a630b5c7f4d00dd4f2a52e7dd0b0","tid":512380,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:05:47.000Z","msg":"要追排名, 改了."},{"pid":"e5c73ef456b719704956f6984b73b5c6e0a95d06","tid":512380,"uid":78769,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:07:05.000Z","msg":"淨係睇字 以為係成間銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e98b407b43e3b0515e4e3267069a885115df677","tid":512380,"uid":30768,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:07:11.000Z","msg":"有咩問題"},{"pid":"8610cca997fb09222d0c4463410382234b00d8e5","tid":512380,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:07:40.000Z","msg":"特登要加中國2個字係大學到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cecd9f4749f826e0c712bc4ac3660436bebb376","tid":512380,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:08:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f164897194940de584b76bf5c7903f21a00c20e","tid":512380,"uid":42764,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1cecd9f4749f826e0c712bc4ac3660436bebb376","tid":512380,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:08:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:15:02.000Z","msg":"符合中國傳統先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連鬼神都用錢收買<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6835564a5740b5e316cc9de29b2d18e8182448b","tid":512380,"uid":86841,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:23:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ee15ad12bf69f634621e135926fbc9d1203a799","tid":512380,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"